317
00:22:45,534 --> 00:22:48,634
Oh, well, the thing is New and I—

318
00:22:48,656 --> 00:22:52,063
Oh, Khao, I have something to tell you.

319
00:22:54,761 --> 00:22:55,442
Well…

320
00:22:56,205 --> 00:23:00,402
We’ve known each other since high school.

321
00:23:01,588 --> 00:23:03,810
I thought it wouldn’t be appropriate back then,

322
00:23:04,853 --> 00:23:06,205
but now that we’re all grown up,

323
00:23:07,896 --> 00:23:09,509
I guess I can be honest with you now.

324
00:23:11,417 --> 00:23:12,014
Sorry?

325
00:23:14,435 --> 00:23:15,515
I like you.

326
00:23:47,880 --> 00:23:51,730
(Is nerd awake yet?)

327
00:23:51,880 --> 00:23:55,850
(No. But I’ll go see him tomorrow.)

328
00:23:55,960 --> 00:23:59,050
(Hope he gets well soon.)

329
00:24:28,602 --> 00:24:29,247
Stop!

330
00:24:30,268 --> 00:24:31,208
Everyone, get up!

331
00:24:35,317 --> 00:24:37,745
