332
00:24:38,632 --> 00:24:40,540
Someone is trying to mess with our faculty.

333
00:24:40,988 --> 00:24:43,906
Our banner has been destroyed.

334
00:24:44,350 --> 00:24:46,605
It was kept in a locked room.

335
00:24:47,131 --> 00:24:48,506
There is no way this is an outside job.

336
00:24:48,678 --> 00:24:49,880
It’s gotta be one of us.

337
00:24:50,494 --> 00:24:52,069
Who? Who did this?

338
00:24:53,402 --> 00:24:55,817
Is it you? Or you? Or you?

339
00:24:58,048 --> 00:24:59,014
Excuse me.

340
00:24:59,779 --> 00:25:01,539
We need the banner by this evening.

341
00:25:01,927 --> 00:25:04,262
If we keep looking for who did it, we’ll never get to use it.

342
00:25:05,896 --> 00:25:08,810
I think it’s better if we make a new one.

343
00:25:09,641 --> 00:25:10,810
Easier said than done!

344
00:25:11,208 --> 00:25:12,903
Who would be able to make a new one in time?

345
00:25:18,957 --> 00:25:20,010
What are you doing?

346
00:25:20,392 --> 00:25:22,220
Painting.

347
00:25:23,520 --> 00:25:26,752
Ann, just paint this whole thing.

348
00:25:27,896 --> 00:25:29,405
Can someone grab me a brush?

349
00:25:31,320 --> 00:25:31,896
Som-O.

350
00:25:31,914 --> 00:25:32,398
Hmm?

351
00:25:32,416 --> 00:25:33,512
Is this the color you want?

352
00:25:33,622 --> 00:25:34,142
Yeah.

353
00:25:34,157 --> 00:25:35,817
Shouldn’t that one be pink?

354
00:25:52,525 --> 00:25:56,007
