358
00:26:08,216 --> 00:26:09,404
I want to see you.

359
00:26:15,155 --> 00:26:16,008
But I know…

360
00:26:17,306 --> 00:26:22,014
You’re here because of New.

361
00:26:26,860 --> 00:26:28,115
