365
00:26:50,822 --> 00:26:52,405
Thank you.

366
00:26:54,200 --> 00:26:55,005
Well…

367
00:26:59,438 --> 00:27:01,306
I really do like you, though.

368
00:27:06,980 --> 00:27:08,374
