369
00:27:18,238 --> 00:27:19,303
They’ll like it.

370
00:27:19,690 --> 00:27:20,517
Don’t worry.

371
00:27:28,048 --> 00:27:29,411
Let me see the banner.

372
00:27:30,875 --> 00:27:34,582
If this doesn’t live up to our faculty’s name, you are all punished.

373
00:27:35,840 --> 00:27:38,330
