374
00:27:40,346 --> 00:27:41,548
Who made it?

375
00:27:49,551 --> 00:27:50,222
It’s beautiful.

376
00:27:50,500 --> 00:27:51,328
Good job.

377
00:27:55,949 --> 00:27:56,620
Som-O.

378
00:27:57,567 --> 00:27:59,872
Som-O, Som-O, Som-O.

379
00:27:59,960 --> 00:28:02,290
Som-O, Som-O, Som-O.

380
00:28:02,342 --> 00:28:03,404
Hold on.

381
00:28:07,105 --> 00:28:08,804
It was a team’s effort.

382
00:28:09,517 --> 00:28:11,976
