392
00:28:41,965 --> 00:28:42,616
Yep.

393
00:28:43,143 --> 00:28:44,084
Wow!

394
00:28:45,813 --> 00:28:46,674
That’s beautiful.

395
00:28:48,325 --> 00:28:49,300
She’s like a pro.

396
00:28:50,521 --> 00:28:53,466
She drew this in a few days, no less.

397
00:28:54,013 --> 00:28:55,927
She’s a genius.

398
00:28:58,810 --> 00:29:00,171
It’s so detailed.

399
00:29:00,968 --> 00:29:02,505
And in so little time.

400
00:29:03,478 --> 00:29:05,813
I didn’t think she was such a great artist.

401
00:29:07,266 --> 00:29:09,106
Yeah, that’s exactly what I want to ask your help with.

402
00:29:16,545 --> 00:29:17,714
Chadjen.

403
00:29:23,826 --> 00:29:24,924
You look so funny.

404
00:29:25,576 --> 00:29:26,573
You look like Sailor Moon a bit.

405
00:29:27,197 --> 00:29:28,934
No, I’m Justice Pao.

406
00:29:29,077 --> 00:29:30,411
But you have a wand.

407
00:29:31,220 --> 00:29:31,906
Here.

408
00:29:39,134 --> 00:29:40,620
Today’s the last day of hazing.

409
00:29:41,065 --> 00:29:42,897
You all have been amazing.

410
00:29:43,755 --> 00:29:45,497
And we’d like to say thank you to all of you

411
00:29:47,216 --> 00:29:49,222
for letting us act all rough and tough these past few days.

412
00:29:50,810 --> 00:29:51,506
Thank you.

413
00:30:02,001 --> 00:30:05,939
Thank you. Thank you. Thank you.

414
00:30:06,072 --> 00:30:08,663
And another thank you to these people who have been helping us out.

415
00:30:10,822 --> 00:30:11,416
Stand up.

416
00:30:17,597 --> 00:30:18,422
Im?

417
00:30:19,789 --> 00:30:22,008
