00:32:07,939 --> 00:32:08,626
It is normal.

446
00:32:13,044 --> 00:32:16,856
(Shark Tao just claimed a gold medal for our nation a few hours ago.)

447
00:32:17,007 --> 00:32:18,311
(Let’s talk to him.)

448
00:32:20,491 --> 00:32:22,528
Oh, it’s Tao.

449
00:32:25,634 --> 00:32:27,625
(A friend of mine is currently unwell…)

450
00:32:29,345 --> 00:32:31,826
(Nerd, get better soon.)

451
00:32:32,462 --> 00:32:33,705
(I’ll come see you when I can.)

452
00:32:37,847 --> 00:32:38,606
(And…)

453
00:32:40,315 --> 00:32:40,976
(Som-O.)

454
00:32:44,517 --> 00:32:47,161
(This gold is yours.)

455
00:33:00,691 --> 00:33:02,370
