00:33:34,847 --> 00:33:36,238
Tao, you jerk.

459
00:33:38,500 --> 00:33:39,213
Chad.

460
00:33:39,474 --> 00:33:40,222
Chadjen.

461
00:33:40,773 --> 00:33:41,423
Chad.

462
00:33:45,413 --> 00:33:46,134
What?

463
00:33:48,936 --> 00:33:50,170
