464
00:33:52,651 --> 00:33:53,499
No. Everything’s fine.

465
00:33:54,906 --> 00:33:57,622
Is it… because of Tao?

466
00:33:58,668 --> 00:33:59,768
Tao?

467
00:34:00,245 --> 00:34:01,114
What about him?

468
00:34:03,940 --> 00:34:04,614
Well…

469
00:34:06,198 --> 00:34:07,511
It’s about that gold.

470
00:34:09,909 --> 00:34:10,629
Isn’t it?

471
00:34:13,004 --> 00:34:13,914
It certainly isn’t.

472
00:34:15,668 --> 00:34:16,557
I’m going to study.

473
00:34:19,287 --> 00:34:19,918
Chad.

474
00:34:22,607 --> 00:34:23,826
