483
00:35:20,874 --> 00:35:26,608
That’s why I told him that I used to like him,

484
00:35:29,014 --> 00:35:31,869
but not anymore,

485
00:35:34,019 --> 00:35:35,810
and I don’t think I ever will.

486
00:35:42,905 --> 00:35:44,318
Because the only person I like…

487
00:35:47,848 --> 00:35:48,903
is you.

488
00:36:01,186 --> 00:36:01,911
New.

489
00:36:49,011 --> 00:36:51,075
I’m sorry I threw it away.

490
00:37:29,912 --> 00:37:30,611
New.

491
00:37:32,653 --> 00:37:33,373
New.

492
00:37:34,025 --> 00:37:34,762
Khao.

493
00:37:49,908 --> 00:37:53,428
What… What did you hear?

494
00:37:55,734 --> 00:37:56,617
Everything.

495
00:38:02,214 --> 00:38:03,511
I’m back, Khao.

496
00:38:45,324 --> 00:38:47,365
Khao, how are we doing?

497
00:38:49,245 --> 00:38:49,835
Oh?

498
00:38:50,222 --> 00:38:50,894
My son!

499
00:38:50,911 --> 00:38:52,317
- New! - My son is alive and well!

500
00:38:52,331 --> 00:38:53,841
Oh, sorry.

501
00:38:54,251 --> 00:38:55,977
Som-O is here.

502
00:38:56,739 --> 00:38:57,720
Are you in pain?

503
00:38:59,271 --> 00:39:00,096
I’m fine now.

504
00:39:01,422 --> 00:39:04,460
He’s back now. Don’t cry.

505
00:39:05,534 --> 00:39:06,400
How are you feeling?

506
00:39:07,088 --> 00:39:08,179
Good.

507
00:39:10,841 --> 00:39:12,228
What’s next on our schedule?

508
00:39:12,862 --> 00:39:13,757
This.

509
00:39:14,044 --> 00:39:16,216
Oh, the difficult class.

510
00:39:16,485 --> 00:39:19,712
Hey, did you see that interview with Shark Tao just now?

511
00:39:19,881 --> 00:39:21,010
He goes to our university, right?

512
00:39:21,417 --> 00:39:22,392
I did see it.

513
00:39:22,598 --> 00:39:24,514
Who is Som-O anyway?

514
00:39:24,768 --> 00:39:25,617
I don’t know.

515
00:39:25,874 --> 00:39:26,628
His girlfriend, maybe?

516
00:39:26,644 --> 00:39:28,444
But it’s so damn romantic.

517
00:39:28,456 --> 00:39:29,979
He really said that on national television, huh?

518
00:39:29,995 --> 00:39:31,918
Now the whole country knows.

519
00:39:32,016 --> 00:39:33,768
It’s on everyone’s social media feed, I bet.

520
00:39:33,777 --> 00:39:34,816
Adorable, isn’t it?

521
00:39:35,068 --> 00:39:36,122
The elevator is here.

522
00:39:38,936 --> 00:39:39,940
Are you coming?

523
00:39:41,419 --> 00:39:42,214
Please go ahead.

524
00:39:53,280 --> 00:39:56,850
(Female Student Dormitory)

525
00:40:01,325 --> 00:40:04,019
- Tao, what are you doing here? - Som.

526
00:40:04,174 --> 00:40:06,149
We were just watching you on TV.

527
00:40:07,133 --> 00:40:08,149
Did you teleport here?

528
00:40:08,771 --> 00:40:10,100
I flew back as soon as the match was over.

529
00:40:14,478 --> 00:40:15,420
I’m here to give you the gold.

530
00:40:21,474 --> 00:40:22,853
A bit much, don’t you think?

531
00:40:23,820 --> 00:40:25,807
Is this all the reason why you’re here?

532
00:40:27,247 --> 00:40:28,220
Of course not.

533
00:40:28,700 --> 00:40:29,805
I’m here to see nerd, too.

534
00:40:30,968 --> 00:40:32,914
Oh, he’s awake!

535
00:40:33,574 --> 00:40:34,314
He is?

536
00:40:34,888 --> 00:40:35,814
I have to see him soon.

537
00:40:40,182 --> 00:40:41,414
But I’m here to see you as well.

538
00:40:46,294 --> 00:40:47,311
Take it.

539
00:40:48,444 --> 00:40:49,608
