541
00:40:59,580 --> 00:41:00,814
You’re always so over the top.

542
00:41:56,146 --> 00:41:58,808
I’ll give you another one if I win.

543
00:42:00,441 --> 00:42:01,968
You don’t have to.

544
00:42:06,050 --> 00:42:07,317
You’re a great athlete.

545
00:42:08,530 --> 00:42:10,847
You won because you’re amazing.

546
00:42:12,253 --> 00:42:13,306
I have nothing to do with it.

547
00:42:14,557 --> 00:42:15,506
Thank you, Som.

548
00:42:17,994 --> 00:42:19,324
Thank you for everything.

549
00:42:27,949 --> 00:42:30,229
Gold, huh?

550
00:42:31,232 --> 00:42:32,737
You’re talented.

551
00:42:33,130 --> 00:42:34,361
Of course.

552
00:42:36,764 --> 00:42:37,708
Isn’t it pretty?

553
00:42:38,402 --> 00:42:39,002
Yeah.

554
00:42:39,533 --> 00:42:41,334
Gold, really?

555
00:42:47,961 --> 00:42:48,576
Chad.

556
00:42:50,237 --> 00:42:51,099
Chadjen!

557
00:42:52,075 --> 00:42:54,130
I asked you what’s wrong.

558
00:42:54,253 --> 00:42:56,142
Let me know so I can apologize.

559
00:42:56,432 --> 00:42:57,862
