561
00:42:58,857 --> 00:43:00,425
What’s with you and him?

562
00:43:00,438 --> 00:43:02,112
I can smell something brewing between you two.

563
00:43:02,471 --> 00:43:05,311
I think I should move in with you, New.

564
00:43:06,117 --> 00:43:08,019
Your Dad would probably be okay with that.

565
00:43:08,597 --> 00:43:09,808
This is hardly a stroll.

566
00:43:09,930 --> 00:43:11,208
It’s like you’re walking away from me.

567
00:43:11,271 --> 00:43:12,694
It’s exhausting.

568
00:43:12,820 --> 00:43:13,856
Are we still talking about the stroll?

569
00:43:14,230 --> 00:43:16,930
We’re talking about my being in love with you.

570
00:43:23,802 --> 00:43:25,374
Some people say

571
00:43:25,505 --> 00:43:28,211
if a couple can ride a bike across this bridge together

572
00:43:28,488 --> 00:43:31,014
without their feet touching the ground once,

573
00:43:31,145 --> 00:43:32,626
they’ll stay together for a really long time.

574
00:43:33,145 --> 00:43:33,960
It means it’s true love.

575
00:43:34,368 --> 00:43:37,811
Tao, Chad and I are dating.

576
00:43:40,162 --> 00:43:41,656
I’m moving out of the college dorm.

577
00:43:41,905 --> 00:43:42,503
Som?

578
00:43:42,937 --> 00:43:43,921
Do you want to move in with me?
